#ooooo

welcome to ooooo cryptovoxels parcel.

We are Japan-based chaotic company held by 2 designers, a film director, a bartender and a management.

We do spatial design, product design, graphic design, bar, films, photographs, music and all the possibilities we imagine to create.

This parcel is evolving continuously.

Hope you enjoy! :)
